Package edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamond.Exception

This package encapsulates all the exception classes we create in the game.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CardNotFoundException
    This exception is thrown when a card is not found.
    InvalidTileTypeException
    This exception is thrown when the tile type is invalid.
    InvalidTimeException
    This exception is thrown when the use time is invalid.
    NoMonsterOnTileException
    This exception is thrown when there is no monster on the tile.
    PlayerCantAccessServerException
    This exception is thrown when a player can't access the server.
    PlayerFullException
    Call this exception when player number reaches maximum.
    ServerPortUnbindException
    This exception is thrown when the server can't bind the port your appointed.
    UsedCardsIsEmptyException
    This exception is thrown when the used cards pile is empty.

Package edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamond.Exception Description

This package encapsulates all the exception classes we create in the game. The game will throw a certain exception when an unexpected input occurs.
Since:
1.2
